  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Cristallo's really popular thanks to its location at the foot of the pistes. It means you can be on the slopes in no time and close to the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea}" title="Sestriere">Sestriere</a> where there's over a hundred shops, bars and restaurants.</p>
<p>This is a modern hotel that's perfect for skiers who want to be in the middle of it all.</p>]]></description>
